title: Best Exclusive Xbox Games Of 2023
description:
In 2023, Xbox-exclusive games had a great year, with five titles standing out from the rest. These are the titles you should play on your Xbox Series X|S. 

In 2023, Xbox-exclusive games had a great year, with five standout titles. These included Forza Motorsport, Hi-Fi Rush, Party Animals, Planet of Lana, and Starfield.

Forza Motorsport, developed by Turn 10 Studios, is a racing simulator with an RPG-style progression system that helps players become better drivers. Hi-Fi Rush, by Tango Gameworks, was a surprise launch and one of the most enjoyable, uplifting, and funny rhythm combat games of the year. Party Animals, by Recrearte Juegos, is a fun party game with a variety of goofy animal characters who compete against each other in a wide range of challenges. Planet of Lana, developed by Wishfully Studios, is a puzzle-platform game with stunning visuals and an immersive story that takes players on a journey to save their sister from an alien invasion. title: MOUSE - Official Early Gameplay Reveal Trailer
description:
Join private detective in MOUSE, a gritty, jazz-fueled shooter. With guns blazing and a retro rubber hose animation style, battle your way through a corrupt city full of crooks and danger. Inspired by classic FPS and noir films, MOUSE is the explosive shooter you've been waiting for.

MOUSE boasts a unique visual style inspired by the charm of 1930s rubber hose animation, transporting players to a nostalgic era of early cartoons. Assume the role of a private detective navigating a noir city teeming with gangs, mobs, and characters from the dark side. Unravel a quest for justice in a noir city mired in chaos, corruption, and vibrant energy, utilizing a diverse arsenal of weapons, power-ups, and explosives to thwart the takeover by corrupt politicians. The game's playful weaponry and distinctive health display, coupled with enemies behaving like cartoon characters, add a lighthearted twist to traditional FPS gameplay.
